# Copy to .env (gitignored) and fill in. NEVER commit real values.

# ── Scout fleet: shared ledger (R7) ──────────────────────────────────────────
# Zero config needed: the fleet reads/writes the OPEN shared ledger at
# registry.brainblast.tech (no token, no key — the server validates submissions).
# Only set this to point at a different registry.
# FLEET_REGISTRY_URL=https://registry.brainblast.tech

# Direct-to-main push of auto-sourced VTIs is opt-in; default prepares a PR.
# FLEET_PUSH policy is read by the brainblast-fleet skill, not a script.
# BRAINBLAST_FLEET_PUSH=main

# ── Marketplace distributor key (only if YOU issue access grants) ─────────────
# ed25519 secret from `brainblast grant keygen`. Verifiers need only the public
# address (BRAINBLAST_MARKET_PUBKEY), which is not secret.
# BRAINBLAST_MARKET_KEY=...
